WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:02.781
Could a woman ever be a journalist?

00:02.781 --> 00:07.388
No, it's dangerous. Look at the manual.

00:07.388 --> 00:10.594
This happened when a woman tried to be a journalist.

00:10.594 --> 00:12.679
Titanic sinking.

00:13.726 --> 00:15.553
What about driving a car?

00:15.553 --> 00:17.198
Driving a car?!

00:17.198 --> 00:19.978
This happened when a woman drove a car.

00:19.978 --> 00:22.523
Hindenburg disaster.

00:22.523 --> 00:24.837
Can a woman ask questions?

00:24.837 --> 00:29.675
Questions? I think it's dangerous.

00:29.675 --> 00:31.961
Ah.
